聽過，太經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係呢部作品入面，沈從文以擅長嘅溫婉嘅文字，講一個湘西民族嘅小故事，呈現獨特嘅湘西民族風情，亦有生死體會、父（爺）愛嘅偉大，情節悲喜混雜，讀落節奏輕快，到結尾仲相當動人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n作品誕生於社會政局動盪嘅上世紀30年代，少咗一份意識形態嘅包袱，但多咗一份純文學嘅質樸，亦體現人性嘅本質，好值得推介比各連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a29ef5a90f826fa1d4198ae869334caafcbf57e1","tid":629776,"uid":68457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T12:40:03.000Z","msg":"今集遇見文學講 舒巷城 嘅《鯉魚門的霧》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我超勁鍾意呢本短篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講香港筲箕灣文學、鄉愁、時移世易嘅反諷，短短十幾頁就能充分呈現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e3602fb22b6fb31468cfa84054dd21cbbb5746","tid":629776,"uid":128164,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T17:40:54.000Z","msg":"1984 George Orwell"},{"pid":"bb9effb2977600845e82549731d128868ca5e6bb","tid":629776,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T18:00:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f987fdc450849b042757f1d118c3a253be6a609","tid":629776,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T18:03:51.000Z","msg":"蒼蠅王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf2f4da0d774ca07cd693297eb09916241180fc","tid":629776,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T18:04:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70b25e23c6a6a3115e8075cd7c70d3b31d2fa099","tid":629776,"uid":72963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0434440aa2a8f2bcc1275acaf7ba0d6fc752a4a","tid":629776,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"ci