c=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c9e78d518dd9d7358fbaaf485b906fff2723d2","tid":629776,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:07:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"254b7a52e2ed1fa3dd28a7502177f18444103ca7","tid":629776,"uid":78460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:11:44.000Z","msg":"Blood and Guts in High School<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/16/171139_b8e5722d2cf6f6b2e6c6ab38a61942b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2F171139_b8e5722d2cf6f6b2e6c6ab38a61942b3.png&h=2a77b41d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一本短短地嘅小說 入面通過性、毒品、暴力等等大膽談論男女不平等、資本主義 係七十年代一本好重要嘅underground literature。裡面短短160頁 作者就多次唔覺唔覺改變寫作format 有日記 有劇本 有第三人稱 有notes 有圖表 等等 雖然文字簡單直接但係非常poetic"},{"pid":"47d798d3b9c6f872f38e040a83d03e3b7460a89d","tid":629776,"uid":33721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:56:53.000Z","msg":"世界末日與冷酷異境<br />\n<br />\n無上面D書學到咁多野<br />\n<br />\n純粹感受下村上描寫既世界"},{"pid":"f6c0f4f4ec46af2832251a057de0f389c5e4083f","tid":629776,"uid":92017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16c5415aef630b74e2c3336836e6e29831d7b55e","tid":629776,"uid":28181,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T12:14:07.000Z","msg":"四代香港人<br />\n全書綜合嬰兒潮世代如何略奪四代香港人資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:44:13.000Z","msg":"當呂大樂一家之言好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係學術界都幾大爭議"},{"pid":"aa494dfda4370f6de0cc4e816d4a733e63331778","tid":629776,"uid":178612,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/16/183611_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.